            <div class="jumia-absolute jumia-bottom-0 jumia-left-0 jumia-right-0 jumia-bg-gradient-to-t jumia-from-black jumia-to-transparent jumia-p-4">
              <p class="jumia-text-white jumia-font-bold">Music & Entertainment</p>
